Tyler.Long.Turo on Instagram 

Thanks for checking out my profile!

   As a Power Host here on the Turo platform a trip with me comes with some guarantees! I always respect everyone’s business and will assure you that I offer 5 Star customer service with professional communication as well as a detailed/reliable car for your trip!

   A quick background of myself, I am from Las Vegas, NV and have lived up and down the west coast! In addition to Turo I am also a Firefighter/EMT and enjoy doing that very much.  I have an extreme passion for cars which  ultimately lead me here to Turo which I am so thankful to be apart of.  My wife and I began hosting with our first car in February 2021 and haven’t stopped since! We try and keep a revolving fleet of new vehicles so whether you are renting for work/business or for your weekend vacation you can do so in style!

   I have personally used Turo on countless occasions including my wedding where I rented a brand new Ford Bronco! Having used Turo myself I know how valuable being a reliable/trustworthy host is. 

  All of our rentals are one hundred percent contactless for both pickup and drop off. The entire process is very streamline and takes hardly anytime at all. Simply show up to the address listed on your reservation, follow the “check in” procedure on Turo, take your pre trip photos and be on your way! For “checkout” you will follow the Turo prompts on the app, take post trip photos, make sure the key is in the car, lock it from the app then on your way! More detailed instructions will be provided upon booking but that is the overall picture when you rent with me!

   I hope to earn your business and share our awesome fleet of cars with you, if you should have any questions and are on Instagram feel free to write me a message on there!
Tyler.Long.Turo

   Take care everyone and safe travels!
